<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Order Delivered</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
<div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
  <h1 style="color: #4CAF50;">Order Delivered! ✅</h1>

  <p>Hi {{userName}},</p>

  <p>Your order #{{orderNumber}} has been successfully delivered!</p>

  <p>We hope you love your purchase. If you have any issues, please don't hesitate to contact us.</p>

  <div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{reviewUrl}}"
       style="background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 12px 30px;
                      text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; display: inline-block;">
      Leave a Review
    </a>
  </div>

  <hr style="border: none; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 30px 0;">

  <p style="color: #999; font-size: 12px; text-align: center;">
    © {{storeName}}. All rights reserved.
  </p>
</div>
</body>
</html>
